    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 at MRL 2. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The output comparison factor demonstrated sufficient agreement with FDA benchmark data to support the regulatory decision, and the overall evidence package supports acceptance of the simulation results for the stated COU.",
